{"tid":615913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N樣大多數人唔驚但你好驚/大多數人驚但你唔驚嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-04-03T18:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T14:45:52.000Z","uid":10039,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f2ea6a63c771500e16de9774ab0bda3a570dd6","tid":615913,"uid":10039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n有羽毛嘅物件/生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論係雞毛掃/雞/鴨/鵝 甚至係麻雀 我都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前係街見到麻雀係我面前 我會停係到 等佢飛走我先敢行<br />\n依家大個好少少 知道只要我向前衝佢地就會飛走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果係唔驚人嘅咕咕雞 我真係會好似傻仔咁dup低頭 兩隻手護住個頭  驚佢飛過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過曱甴我又唔驚 成屋尖叫嘅時候 得我一個夠膽就咁攞紙巾一嘢啪落去殺左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爽呀！"},{"pid":"8d458b1c7d7bfcee0f17c8a555cf704d86dde2b5","tid":615913,"uid":10039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:49:32.000Z","msg":"其實係想上黎R下水吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未瞓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a10bb5b4a2c1d4b2d16f6053cf1e43289d1eb96","tid":615913,"uid":37199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"唔驚老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73459a8080a7cc623f9290eb39472ff18957db9d","tid":615913,"uid":10039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a10bb5b4a2c1d4b2d16f6053cf1e43289d1eb96","tid":615913,"uid":37199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:51:13.000Z","msg":"唔驚老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T18:52:43.000Z","msg":"依個我都ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只要佢唔會追住我黎咬就得<br />\n咁你驚咩"},{"pid":"33b03d75ae4c19d81290ee449d2df00